sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Trainer Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS (self-signed)
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>trainer-controller-manager
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pods<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(PodMonitor)
    participant Metrics as Metrics Endpoint<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Metrics: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation and Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS (self-signed)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Controller reconciliation loop
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>Resolve runtime reference<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime spec

    Controller->>K8sAPI: SSA Apply JobSet CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: JobSet created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup CR<br/>(if gang-scheduling enabled)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: PodGroup created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update NetworkPolicy<br/>(RHAI per-TrainJob isolation)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: NetworkPolicy applied

    Note over Controller,TrainingPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking

    Controller->>K8sAPI: List Pods for TrainJob<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod IPs (ready pods)

    loop Poll training metrics (periodic)
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/28080 plaintext<br/>Auth: NetworkPolicy-restricted
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Training progress metrics
    end

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update TrainJob annotation<br/>trainer.opendatahub.io/trainerStatus<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Prometheus,Metrics: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scrape

    Prometheus->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS (self-signed)<br/>insecureSkipVerify
    Metrics-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
